Class ViewManager.ViewReceipt

  • java.lang.Object
    • cinnamon.engine.system.ViewManager.ViewReceipt
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Position, Size
    Enclosing class:
    ViewManager

    public class ViewManager.ViewReceipt
extends Object
implements Position, Size

    Acts as an immutable copy of a ViewManager.View. ViewReceipts are passed across threads when drawing information is sent to the Canvas instead of the View itself.
